description:
Feel the coolest vibes of street fashion brought to your wardrobe by latest DLC fashion pack for Fashion World: the "Street Style" Pack. The game of a stylish adventure just got better, with 20 additional levels of interesting tasks in the creation of trendy street looks.

Bring on the energy and creativity from the street into your style with the Street Style Pack, taking on the globe in fashion style.
name: Fashion World DLC 2: Street Style
